Stocks posted broad gains on hopes that Russia/Ukraine tensions may defuse.

Dow ends +422, +1.2% to 34,988. Techs led, lifting Nasdaq +2.5%. S&P +1.6%. Oil prices eased.

But bond yields rose on stronger-than-expected wholesale inflation data.  10-year T-note 2.05% vs 1.99% Mon.
